data.description: Welcome home to Imagine! This boutique community of spacious, modern farmhouse homes is located right in the heart of Phoenix. This home was built in 2022 and has it all - high ceilings, wood-look tile floors, white shaker cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Downstairs you'll find an open-concept floorplan perfect for entertaining...spacious chef's kitchen that flows easily into the living room and indoor/outdoor living feel with huge glass sliding doors. Upstairs is a generous primary suite with soaking tub and walk-in closet as well as 3 other bedrooms, balcony, hall bath, and laundry room. Top it all off with a 3-car garage! Unheard of in the central city! The community is gated and features a luxurious pool and cute picnic area. Plan your tour today!
